Finally found a use for igtv lmao 😂
I'll be posting my music here from now on! This is on spotify btw! ✨

🎶Music: the path of the wind - vitamin string quartet cover

'Jujutsu Kaisen' 👻 (saves & shares appreciated!)
Fixed the characters' scaling issues and reposted! Yesterday's post got removed for the music unfortunately. 🥲 Can you name all the characters?
Live wallpaper will be up on my Patreon later tonight! Prints will be coming in 2 weeks!
30 minutes of coloring help from @isaaawuu 🥸
